original: Jansson, Sven Wilhelm, komminister, Dals Grinstad, f. 27/10/01 i Åmål av Julius J. o. Sabina Pettersson. — Stud:ex. i Gbg 22, teol. fil. ex. 23, teol. kand. 26, prakt. teol. ex. samt prästv. f. Karlstads stift 27. Missiv i Östervallskog, Grinstad, Torp o. Svanskog, tf. kommin. i Svanskog, kommin. i Grinstad sed. 37. Ordf. i kyrkostämma o. skolstyr.
translated: Jansson, Sven Wilhelm, minister, Dals Grinstad, b. 27/10/01 in Åmål to Julius J. and Sabina Pettersson. — Passed student examination in Gothenburg in 1922, theological bachelor's degree in 1923, theological candidate in 1926, practical theological examination, and ordained priest for the Diocese of Karlstad in 1927. Served in Östervallskog, Grinstad, Torp, and Svanskog, acting minister in Svanskog, minister in Grinstad since 1937. Chairman of the church assembly and school board.
